review.reviewBody: this place is my favorite Butter Chicken (GF)  and Spinach and Paneer Naan in Vancouver! Good portion sizes and excellent flavour!
everything was sooo amazing! the fact that it doesn't come with rice isn't a big deal if you get the 2 for 1 garlic Naan, they were sooooo big. great portions too
I love this place, chick Chicken Tikka Masala (GF), Saag Paneer (GF) and Garlic Naan are excellent.
Amazing and the naan is hands down best ever had! I highly recommend this restaurant
the food is excellent. Vegetable Samosa tasty and largeLamb Rogan Josh (DF, GF) Chicken Tandoori (GF) very tasty and arrives sizzling to your table. A truly lovely place to attend or order from
